  <summary><![CDATA['A little blog TLC' - a blog post by Darren Ferguson about Examine, Umbraco, Lucene, Lucene.net, Base, AJAX written on 13th April B25AC8DE-26FC-44E7-BB89-F200B2327094]]></summary>
